&lt;li>Install iBus and related libraries&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>yay -S ibus ibus-m17n m17n-db
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>Download Swanalekha inpput method lib and copy to to &lt;code>/usr/share/m17n/&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>wget http://swanalekha.smc.org.in/m17n/ml-swanalekha.mim
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo cp ml-swanalekha.mim /usr/share/m17n/ml-swanalekha.mim
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="3">
&lt;li>Start ibus daemon&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>ibus-daemon -drxR
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="4">
&lt;li>Open ibus preferences&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>ibus-setup
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="5">
&lt;li>Switch to Input Method Tab, Click Add and search for &lt;code>Malayalam - ml-swanalekha&lt;/code> and add it. If needed, change hotkey for switching input methods.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Restart ibus daemon&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>ibus-daemon -rdx
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Also ensure that you have some malayalam fonts installed in your system. Fonts are available from:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>